email.possibleFraudFooter: Tobetsa mo kgokagannyong ya setšhaba ka tlase, tsena jaaka admin mme o tlhophe Fraud management mo lenaaneng.
email.possibleFraudSubHeader: Palo ya ditiragalo tse ka kgonegang tsa tsietso ka tekanyetso ya 75% ya tsietso
email.possibleFraudInformation: Sistimi ya rona e ikemetseng e lemogile ditiragalo tse ka kgonegang tsa tsietso. O ka sekaseka ka botlalo ka fao Community admin interface. Ditiragalo dingwe tsa mofuta ono di ka nna tsa se na mabaka a tsietso ka jalo ela tlhoko go sekaseka ka botlalo pele o phimola dikakanyo.
email.possibleFraudHeader: Tiragalo e ka kgonegang ya tsietso
email.automaticToxicityDetection: Dikakanyo tseno di tshwayeditswe ka boiketsetso jaaka di le botlhaswa ka go dirisa AI algorithms e e lekanyang botlhaswa jwa dikakanyo. O ka phimola dikakanyo fa go tlhokega.
email.automaticToxicityDetectionVision: AI algorithm ka boiketsetso e tshwayeditse ditshwantsho tse di amanang le dikakanyo tseno. Algorithm eno e sekaseka ditshwantsho go bona fa di na le ditshwantsho tsa batho ba baholo, thubakanyo, tsa kalafi, le tse di tseneletseng. O ka phimola dikakanyo fa go tlhokega.
email.automaticToxicityDetectionDisclaimer: Ka dinako tse dingwe algorithm ya AI e bala mananeo a fosahetseng, mo maemong ao o seke wa tshwenyega, ga o tlhoke go tsaya kgato epe mme o ka tlhokomologa imeile eno.
